          Web Development & <span class="text-amber-400">Automation Services</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 mb-8">
          I help businesses work smarter with technology. Websites, apps, automation, and hosting. Built properly, priced fairly, delivered on time.
        </p>
        <a href="/#services" class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg inline-block">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-stagger>

        <!-- Websites -->
