          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-ai-purple transition-colors">Business Process Automation</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-ai-purple font-medium mb-3">From ¬£799</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Automate the repetitive tasks that eat into your day. Invoicing, emails, data entry, and scheduling. Let technology handle the routine work.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            {["Invoice & data processing", "Email automation", "Workflow integration", "Works with your existing tools"].map(feature => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success-green mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
