          <p class="text-sm text-ai-purple font-medium mb-3">From ¬£99/month</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Reliable hosting with regular backups, security updates, and support when you need it. I keep your site running so you can focus on your business.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            {["Daily backups", "Security updates", "Performance monitoring", "Email support"].map(feature => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success-green mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
